@startuml Export Process Sequence
' Simplified Export and Download Flow

actor User
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "Backend" as API
participant "PDF Generator" as PDF
participant "Audio Generator" as Audio
participant "File System" as FS

== PDF Export ==
User -> FE: Export PDF
FE -> API: PDF request
API -> PDF: Generate PDF
PDF -> FS: Save PDF file
PDF -> API: File path
API -> FE: Download link
FE -> User: Download PDF

== Audio Book Export ==
User -> FE: Export Audio Book
FE -> API: Audio request
API -> Audio: Generate narration
Audio -> FS: Save audio files
Audio -> API: File paths
API -> FE: Download link
FE -> User: Download audiobook

== File Download ==
User -> FE: Download file
FE -> FS: Request file
FS -> FE: File data
FE -> User: File download

@enduml
